description: We don't make any exaggerated claims about our HDMI cable, but we stand by every inch. OSD Audio has the best price on HDMI for high definition TVs, 3D TVs, DVD players, computers and more. We promise you that when you buy OSD HDMI cable, it will perform as well as the high-priced designer brands. Features durable gold-plated internal shield, corrosion-resistant 24K gold contacts, supports 1440p for 3D TV applications, supports 1080p resolution and has a 10.2Gbps transfer rate.
title: OSD Audio High Speed HDMI Cable with Ethernet v1.4, 100 Feet
